{"tid":1817604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"禁蒙面法被裁定無效政府不服提上訴　法院展開聆訊","createTime":"2020-01-09T08:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T10:54:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d81086b67eca633d8b55497443cac09549ceb96","tid":1817604,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"高等法院原訟庭去年11月裁定《緊急法》及《禁蒙面法》部分條文違憲，並宣布《禁蒙面法》無效，政府不服上訴，上訴聆訊今日起一連兩天展開。<br />\n<br />\n民主派立法會議員和社民連梁國雄在原訟庭取得司法覆核勝訴，法律界議員郭榮鏗在開庭前表示，政府上訴尋求推翻原訟庭判決，以繼續執行《禁蒙面法》，但他認為當局應該撤回上訴。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗認為，《禁蒙面法》已經證明無助解決政治爭議，反而深化社會矛盾，加上武漢不明肺炎正影響香港，人人都爭相買口罩、戴口罩，當局不應一錯再錯，置市民的健康不理。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501805-20200109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501805-20200109.htm&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF03hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=485201c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501805-20200109.htm&h=74281ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501805-20200109.htm</a>"},{"pid":"60f3bce276212c9bbf052f08e4f3eb10e3989b9b","tid":1817604,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF03hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=0152d1d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">少左好多人rt <br />\n唔好鬆懈呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7067345776f984ca100a89868e6c24d5cc9c622c","tid":1817604,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10: